maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Midday” game were:
03-06-13-14-21-22-24-25-26-46-49-52-53-59-63-68-70-71-76-77, BE: 14
(three, six, thirteen, fourteen, twenty-one, twenty-two, twenty-four, twenty-five, twenty-six, forty-six, forty-nine, fifty-two, fifty-three, fifty-nine, sixty-three, sixty-eight, seventy, seventy-one, seventy-six, seventy-seven; BE: fourteen)
